data.chText: 抗菌素；抗生素（如青霉素）
data.enText: a substance, for example penicillin , that can destroy or prevent the growth of bacteria and cure infections
The doctor put her on antibiotics (= told her to take them) .

simple_means.memory_skill: anti 抗 + bio 生命 + tic 有…性质的 → 抗生素的

tr: a chemical substance derivable from a mold or bacterium that can kill microorganisms and cure bacterial infections
example: when antibiotics were first discovered they were called wonder drugs

tr: of or relating to antibiotic drugs

value.def: Antibiotics are medical drugs used to kill bacteria and treat infections.

example.ex: Your doctor may prescribe a course of antibiotics.
example.tran: 你的医生可能会开一个疗程的抗生素。
